{"name":"Saint Karl's Chaplet of Everlasting Life","type":"misc","img":"modules/morkborg-3p/images/icons/misc/prayer-beads.png","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>Has 3d6 beads. Whenever you would be broken, roll d6 instead. Up to that many beads break and you restore hp equal to the amount broken.</p>","carryWeight":0.05,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7liZlUNfTdrLYETW":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.44T3QdleDRPHYYMP"}},"_id":"21auk7jpfoFpXN9d"}
{"name":"Holiest Water","type":"misc","img":"systems/morkborg/icons/items/misc/potion.png","data":{"containerSpace":0.1,"description":"<p>Water that burns anything. Successfully splashing it (Presence) deals d8 damage this round and the next. d6+presence charges. The flask that holds the water is the relic.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","carryWeight":0.1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7liZlUNfTdrLYETW":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.TTMYwmnVZptsL5Sm"}},"_id":"5WZU7cFrqEgHKORf"}
{"name":"Crucifix of the Dead","type":"misc","img":"systems/morkborg/icons/items/misc/crucifix_silver.png","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>A massive golden crucifix mounted with a small skeleton. Undead tolerate you, no roll required. The same cannot always be said for your companions. Heavy enough to require both hands and deal d8 damage, doubled against undead.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7liZlUNfTdrLYETW":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.W3yIUg4raOJuPzT8"}},"_id":"6uOiiKEnvj8Tj5BA"}
{"name":"Basilisk Miter","type":"misc","img":"systems/morkborg/icons/classitems/mitre.png","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>A miter sanctified by HE, looking at it inspires awe. Those staring at it must test Presence at the start of their turn or continue staring, becoming paralyzed for d4 days after 3 failures in a row. After a success a creature is immune to the effect.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7liZlUNfTdrLYETW":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.5gqOmrpc7VranWVO"}},"_id":"IdqNrh3YsbyPz1VT"}
{"name":"Saint Brita's Purging Sword","type":"weapon","img":"systems/morkborg/icons/items/weapons/sword.png","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>D6, DR 10 to attack. Deals double damage to wielders of unclean scrolls, undead, and demons. Deals triple damage on critical hits. Will attack you (DR 14 to defend) if you commit heresy, until you repent or die.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1,"damageDie":"1d6","handed":"1","weaponType":"melee"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7liZlUNfTdrLYETW":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.AlSKg5YyLsI2ubxb"}},"_id":"LAXFY8VDPtqdRaG5"}
{"name":"Werna's Shield of Faith","type":"shield","img":"systems/morkborg/icons/items/armor/shield.png","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>An ornamented shield that reflects damage back to attackers. All damage blocked by the shield and your armor is dealt back to your attacker.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7liZlUNfTdrLYETW":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.DTjb5xc1sFaKYscd"}},"_id":"LHau0mxv4XDNjClo"}
