{"name":"Saint Pelle's Apocrypha","type":"misc","img":"systems/morkborg/icons/classitems/blasphemousbible.png","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>A heavily crossed out, edited, and written over work, writing in it can alter past or future events. Use a power and test Presence DR 16 to write in the Apocrypha, altering the course of past events or nudging future events on a certain course. You can&rsquo;t stop the end of the world. On a success, the change becomes reality in some form or another. Failure causes a Misery. Critical failure causes the end of the world.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7liZlUNfTdrLYETW":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.WPwf53DgdeTzbzkJ"}},"_id":"v5ctssTqpOu7NfFd"}
{"name":"The Arm of Saint Johan","type":"misc","img":"modules/morkborg-3p/images/icons/misc/arm.png","data":{"containerSpace":1,"description":"<p>A gilded arm, set in a mahogany box. It can be asked questions about the world and will always answer truthfully, in what way an arm can. Grows tired after being asked Presence + d4 questions a day.</p>","carryWeight":1,"equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7liZlUNfTdrLYETW":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.5sfCQfhN63yQtEqa"}},"_id":"xFy8YUQ1lzMkAmub"}
